{"tid":15389,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李國章：撐港獨與撐特朗普無異","createTime":"2016-12-01T03:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T14:04:26.000Z","uid":11001,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d9898974ca8df537096a9f91d6cee977ad4760","tid":15389,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:16:46.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】港大校委會主席李國章昨出席港大畢業生議會的閉門論壇，近百校友及教員出席。李國章在會上批評「討論港獨是完全浪費時間」，港獨本身亦絕不理性，認為年輕人支持港獨，是由於對現存建制感沮喪，形容與支持英國脫歐和特朗普當美國總統的人無異。<br />\n<br />\n與校友閉門論壇 百人出席<br />\n<br />\n出席論壇的立法會議員葉建源會後反駁，指李國章應尊重學生獨立思考，自己雖不讚成港獨，但大學應讓學生討論，即使批評一件事，也要經討論才能批評。<br />\n<br />\n今次是李國章年初上任校委會主席後首次出席畢業生議會的大型交流活動，約兩小時的論壇氣氛平和。李在開場白稱，港大近年的國際排名一直下跌，是因為變得自滿，缺乏競爭意識。<br />\n<br />\n李形容一些平庸的教員，以學術自由為名掩飾自己的無能，將任何對他們的批評當成干預學術自由，以保教席，但他不見出色的教員會作如此控訴。他反問學術自由受損有何實例，如是否有課程和研究因政治壓力被取消，或學術刊物被抽起。<br />\n<br />\n斥平庸教員以學術自由掩飾無能<br />\n<br />\n在問答環節，有教員批評李國章公開指摘教員無能並不恰當，李回應稱自己不能取悅所有人，只能以公開批評（name and shame）促使教員改進。<br />\n<br />\n有今年畢業的校友表明支持港獨，反問李為何能在論壇面對校友，但年初校委會會議時卻不面對大樓外的示威學生，李答稱因當時示威學生是「暴徒」。該校友反駁港大校長馬斐森當時面對學生亦能全身而退。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否覺得自己在校內有信任問題，李稱自己唯一可做的是盡力做出成績，形容因他被特首委任便是壞人的想法愚蠢。李國章最後被問到會否參選特首，他以中文稱自己「與世無爭」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00002/1480528948514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00002%2F1480528948514&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq4scwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=1ee823e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00002%2F1480528948514&h=b7ee6fba\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00002/1480528948514</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">曲到圓</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf267f059988fa2bfeaa4d534da0b0e53a0dd1a","tid":15389,"uid":20898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:22:23.000Z","msg":"支那人好撚橕特朗普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32f4cc34601c07b9c170cbfa38b065ec9a5dd2e","tid":15389,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:22:35.000Z","msg":"呢條柒碌<br />\n即係話港獨同侵侵都係得到民意受權啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n捉去打靶啦"},{"pid":"6b42552475761d4fc0330df0ac6796e491153d94","tid":15389,"uid":714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"啫係美國有幾千萬人撐港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28b4bc945152f01fbe7d3f4e482e526a94faa83","tid":15389,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即係有機會成真</span>"},{"pid":"39dc8f13589c1cfb32bcf689d3d103181a4fda1d","tid":15389,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即係有機會成真</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係一定會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f9a976acfd66b3f898dd9e0f5a1aa724c649b8","tid":15389,"uid":24759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:29:45.000Z","msg":"原來禁多美國人撐港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f7b0424e70b40345aadce45cae6a303abec5b6","tid":15389,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: large;\">即係有機會成真</span></blockquote><br